A MAN who was acting "suspiciously" is being hunted by police. 'Suspicious' man sparks police hunt A MAN who was acting "suspiciously" is being hunted by police.Locals in Greenock were alarmed by the man's behaviour and called police to report the incident.Police Scotland is appealing for the help of the public in tracing the man was seen in Murdieston Dam last Wednesday evening.He is described as Asian, between 30 and 40, with black hair.Anyone with information should call 101. 